videos.description: Malachi Flynn thinks he has the open layup, but Daniel Gafford comes over and swats the shot off the backboard.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Gafford rises for the block on Flynn) 2021/05/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gafford rises for the block on Flynn

videos.description: Khem Birch denies Bradley Beal's layup attempt leading to Pascal Siakam finishing the layup plus the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Siakam finishes the and-1 after the Birch block) 2021/05/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Siakam finishes the and-1 after the Birch block

videos.description: Russell Westbrook drops the dime to Alex Len for the one-handed jam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Westbrook finds a sprinting Len for the jam) 2021/05/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Westbrook finds a sprinting Len for the jam

videos.description: Garrison Mathews knocks down the 3-pointer from way downtown while being fouled.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Mathews cashes 3 plus the foul) 2021/05/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mathews cashes 3 plus the foul

videos.description: Pascal Siakam finds a running Khem Birch for the huge two-handed jam late in the fourth.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Siakam rips pass to Birch for late 4th quarter dunk) 2021/05/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Siakam rips pass to Birch for late 4th quarter dunk

videos.description: Russell Westbrook finishes the layup in the lane bringing him one short of Oscar Robertson for most career triple-doubles.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Westbrook notches 180th career triple-double with this layup) 2021/05/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Westbrook notches 180th career triple-double with this layup

videos.description: Fred VanVleet has defenders all over him as he knocks down the 3-pointer sending the game to overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (VanVleet hits tough 3 to send game to OT) 2021/05/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: VanVleet hits tough 3 to send game to OT

videos.description: Bradley Beal gets the huge and-1 with under a minute remaining, which helps the Wizards take down the Raptors in overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Beal’s clutch and-1 leads Wizards to OT win) 2021/05/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Beal's clutch and-1 leads Wizards to OT win
